      "html": "\n  <div class=\"clip-section-title\">Step 5. Google AI Studio 접속</div>\n  <div class=\"clip-section-content\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--text-body);margin-bottom:12px\">주소창에 <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>aistudio.google.com</strong></a>을 입력하여 이동합니다.</p>\n    <div style=\"margin:16px 0;border-radius:var(--radius);overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border)\">\n      <img src=\"https://i.imghippo.com/files/nzDx9281SrI.jpg\" alt=\"AI Studio 접속 화면\" style=\"width:100%;display:block\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-muted);padding:8px 12px;background:var(--bg-offwhite);border-top:1px solid var(--border)\">브라우저 주소창에 aistudio.google.com 입력</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n"
